title: nightmare
description:
the nightmare by lars kepler

of violins, arms smuggling and making a deal with the devil.


Four bigwits celebrate the closing of an arms deal that would cirmuvent an arms embargo to civil war torn Sudan. 

The participants are bound by what is called a paganini contract, a precarious balancing of desires and fears.

A picture is secretly taken and leaked to a female peace activist.Her boyfriend tries to blackmail one of the four persons in the picture. 

A grob is assigned to enforce the pagagini contract and retrieve the photo.

the preface is devoted to music and musical geniuses, string music is a constant undercurrent and the villain is hard to resist.


Could anyone ever guess what musical piece is performed by examining a photo of musicians playing? 


bit rate 48kbps
